`text=''` becomes `text=""`: empty values re-emit with double quotes.

Why: the AST records the value without its quote style, and the canonical
quoting chain tries double quotes first.

* Covers: serializeAttribute in $:/plugins/tiddlywiki/wikitext-serialize/utils/parsetree.js.
* Mode: ast-only (the Input field withholds the source from the serializer).
